please remember this ! !!!!


python -m pip install fastapi uvicorn sqlalchemy "psycopg[binary]" python-dotenv



fastapi — builds your API
uvicorn — runs your FastAPI application
sqlalchemy — lets Python communicate with and manage SQL databases
psycopg[binary] — PostgreSQL driver used by SQLAlchemy
python-dotenv — loads your database URL from .env


if you are also building pytest 

python -m pip install pytest


then record everything 

python -m pip freeze > requirements.txt